    {
      "author": "Marjan Hadiyan",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107673137076748275281?hl=id",
      "rating": 3,
      "text": "My first time at The Coffee Beans, I ordered Medium Café Latte. Surprisingly it's large (for me) enough for a day (and more) coffee. It's creamy which is good, although i don't know what kind of beans the serve. Outdoor seating is right next to a pond which gives relaxing vibes. Has various menu to choose from, coffee, tea, snack and dessert.",
      "textTranslated": "Ini pertama kalinya saya ke The Coffee Beans, saya memesan Medium Café Latte. Anehnya, ukurannya besar (bagi saya), cukup untuk minum kopi seharian (dan lebih). Teksturnya creamy, yang bagus, meskipun saya tidak tahu jenis biji kopi apa yang mereka gunakan. Tempat duduk di luar ruangan berada tepat di sebelah kolam yang memberikan suasana santai. Tersedia berbagai pilihan menu, kopi, teh, camilan, dan makanan penutup.",
      "date": "2017-11-25T03:09:19.065Z",
      "relativeDate": "8 tahun lalu",
      "likesCount": 1,
